[This report highlight the difficulties of achieving high vaccine
coverage in populations with a high proportion of migrant workers.
The report from Shenzhen indicates that some success is being
achieved following the implementation of a free national immunisation
strategy targeting measles and 10 other major diseases.

The location of the city of Shenzhen in Guangdong province, close to
the border with the Hong Kong SAR., can be viewed at
<http://encarta.msn.com/map_701512798/guangdong.html>.
The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of China can be accessed at
<http://healthmap.org/promed?g=1795565&v=30.5,103.9,4>. - Mod.CP]
